            <div class="content">
              <h2 id="ielts-table">IELTS Band Score to CRS Points Table 2026</h2>
              <div class="section-label">IELTS General Training only — Academic is NOT accepted for Express Entry</div>
              <p>This table shows the CRS points for every IELTS General Training band score, including the equivalent CLB level. All four skills (Listening, Reading, Writing, Speaking) are scored separately. Use the <a href="https://crsscorecalculator.vercel.app/ielts-crs-calculator">IELTS to CRS Calculator</a> to enter your individual skill scores.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="tabs">
              <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab(this,'ielts-1st')">1st Language (Max pts)</button>
              <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab(this,'ielts-2nd')">2nd Language (Bonus pts)</button>
            </div>
            <div class="tab-wrap">
              <div class="tab-panel active" id="tab-ielts-1st">
                <div style="overflow-x:auto;">
                  <table style="min-width:580px;">
                    <thead>
                      <tr>
                        <th>IELTS Band Score</th>
                        <th>CLB Level</th>
                        <th>CRS pts/skill (No Spouse)</th>
                        <th>CRS pts/skill (With Spouse)</th>
