            <p class="tiny muted" style="margin-top:16px;">Disclaimer: CRS language points shown are based on the official <a href="https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/express-entry/eligibility/criteria-comprehensive-ranking-system/grid.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">IRCC CRS Grid</a>. Always verify your CLB equivalency with the official IRCC language testing page and consult a regulated Canadian immigration consultant (RCIC) before making immigration decisions. Test score ranges may change — verify current ranges with your test provider.</p>

